$$
\widetilde{\mathfrak{S}}_{0,3}^+ \xrightarrow{\varphi_0'} \operatorname{Sl}(2, \hat{\mathbf{Z}})' \subset \operatorname{Gl}(2, \hat{\mathbf{Z}}) \leqno{(4)}
$$
et l'homomorphisme
$$
